FOLDERS STRUCTURE :
	- "rosick/common" : package with common files used by all the tutorials.
	- "rosick/mckesson" : package with Java porting of Jason McKesson OpenGL tutorials.
	

	
USAGE WITH ECLIPSE IDE :
To test the tutorials, copy or link the "rosick" package into an existing project (in the "src" folder).
If you haven't already done, in the project build path add and configure the lwjgl library (visit http://www.lwjgl.org/ for further information).



